## Everything we know begins with a sensation.
Let's rediscover the world through our five senses!

> **_"Nothing exists in our intelligence that was not first in our senses."_**
>
> Democritus

What could be more vibrant than feeling the warmth of the sun, the different textures of sand, the scents of the lagoon, oriental flavours and watching the colours of the sky change hour by hour?

For this 6th edition of our walks and retreats in the Sahara, by the sea, I invite [Michèle Gay](https://www.linkedin.com/in/ACoAAADg_hkBVuVT0dOQGU6E-D6v7qnmDDpVNj0), culinary perfumer and wonderful storyteller, to heighten our senses.

Silence, simplicity and disconnection will bring these to the fore.

Each day, I will take you through a new landscape and propose a different way to make it dialogue with you.

Each day, Michèle will take you on a different sensory journey and accompany you in capturing its essence.

Marie Emmanuelle

* * *

### Sense, the senses, the essence.
Blank slate for Michèle Gay.

**From 16 to 23 November 2024**
at the edge of the lagoon of **Dakhla**, Morocco.
